Class UndergraduateStudent

  • java.lang.Object
    • people.Person
      • people.PartTimeEmployee
        • people.UndergraduateStudent

  • public class UndergraduateStudent
extends PartTimeEmployee

    Contains undergraduate student attributes and algorithms to modify the attributes. Is considered a PartTimeEmployee.

    Depends on:

    • PartTimeEmployee

    Undergraduate student - a student at a college or university who has not yet earned a bachelor's or equivalent degree.

    1.0 (05/09/2017)

    Author:
